This is the motion function block used to control all the axes. Due to some differences in the control part for different types of motion and drives, there are additional conditions in some parts of the code.
Important things to check if the drive is not moving: - homing - motion lock from add ons (capping station, no go zones) - door sensors - operation mode - communication with the drives (Online access)
Changed jogging limits to prevent overshooting
